  <brief_title>Intravenous Enhancin[Co-amoxiclav] Versus Postoperative Enhancin in Prevention of Postadenotonsillectomy Morbidity.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Single Intraoperative Intravenous Enhancin[Co-amoxiclav] Versus Postoperative Full Oral Course in Prevention of Post Adenotonsillectomy Morbidity:A Randomised Clinical Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
