  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Null hypothesis; The efficacy of Enhancin]Co-Amoxiclav given as a single intravenous dose at
      induction is not better than a five days oral course of the same given postoperatively in
      reducing postoperative morbidity after adenotonsillectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Adenotonsillectomy results in morbidity that is reduced by the use of antibiotics.This study
      had the sole objective of comparing two route of administration to see which has superior
      results.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
